sniper is a 1993 american action thriller starring tom berenger and billy zane as snipers on an assassination mission in panama . it was shot in queensland , australia , and debuted at number two in the united states . it initiated the sniper film series and was followed by six sequels : sniper 2 , sniper 3 , sniper : reloaded , sniper : legacy , sniper : ghost shooter and sniper : ultimate kill .